## Attribution

This Skill draws inspiration from the public work of Walter Isaacson,
including his biographical methodology as expressed in his books, interviews,
and public lectures. This is a tribute and educational application, not an
official endorsement.

Isaacson's works referenced:
- Steve Jobs (2011)
- Elon Musk (2023)
- Einstein: His Life and Universe (2007)
- Leonardo da Vinci (2017)
- Benjamin Franklin: An American Life (2003)
- The Code Breaker: Jennifer Doudna (2021)
- Lex Fridman Podcast #395 (2023)
- NEH Jefferson Lecture
- Various interviews and public speeches
